'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da cewa suna kama da muppets
Wasu daga cikin 'yan majalisar sun yi mamakin shawarar da aka yi na sauya sunansu zuwa CHUP (mambobin majalisar dokokin Wales).
Wannan shawarar ta samo asali ne daga shirye-shiryen sauya sunan Majalisar zuwa 'Majalisar Wales'.
Mambobin jam'iyyar daga ko'ina cikin siyasa suna fargabar cewa wannan zai iya zama abin dariya.
Wani dan Labour ya ce kungiyarsa ta damu da cewa sabon sunan yana da "Tup" da "Vdlub".
Ga masu karatu da ba na Wales ba: A yaren Welsh, wannan yana da ma'ana mai banƙyama.
A cewar wani dan jam'iyyar Plaid, dukan kungiyar ba ta farin ciki kuma ta ba da wasu hanyoyin.
Wani wakilin jam'iyyar Conservative Party of Wales ya nuna cewa kungiyarsa  ba ta da son zuciya game da canjin sunan, amma ya lura cewa sabon sunan  MWP yana da wasu kamanceceniya da  mumpet.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta harafin Welsh W kamar yadda ake furta harafin U a Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda ke shirya tsarin dokar da za ta sauya sunan, ya yi wannan sanarwa: Tabbas, yanke shawara ta ƙarshe game da duk wasu sunaye masu bayyanawa da za a kira membobin Majalisar za ta kasance ga membobin kansu.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba Majalisar Wales ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani bincike na jama'a kan shawarwarin da suka nuna cewa akwai goyon baya sosai ga kiran Majalisar 'Parliament of Wales'.
Game da mukamin mambobinta, Hukumar ta fi son 'yan majalisar dokokin Wales, a takaice CHUP, amma zaɓi CHUP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya bayan yin tambayoyin jama'a.
'Yan majalisar sun ba da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma samun yarjejeniya a fili zai zama ciwon kai ga shugaban kasa Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da takardar dokar sauyawa cikin makonni.
Dokar ta sake fasalin za ta kuma haɗa da wasu canje-canje ga yadda Majalisar ke aiki, ciki har da dokokin da ke hana 'yan majalisar zama, da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
'Yan majalisar za su sami kuri'ar karshe kan yadda za a kira su idan aka kai ga tattauna dokar.
