Wani yaro ɗan shekara 13 ya ji rauni sa'ad da wani ɗan kifi ya yi kifi a California
Wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai wa wani yaro dan shekara 13 hari a ranar Asabar da ta gabata yayin da yake nutsewa don neman lobster a California a ranar farko ta kakar farauta, in ji hukumomin da ke wakiltar jihar.
An kai harin ne a kusa da bakin rairayin bakin teku na Beacon a Encinitas, jim kadan kafin karfe 7 na safe.
Chad Hummel ya shaida wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa yana ruwa da abokai na tsawon rabin sa'a a safiyar Asabar, lokacin da ya ji yaron yana kuka don taimako, sai ya shiga tare da wasu mutane don su fitar da shi daga cikin ruwan.
Da farko, Hamel ya yi tunanin cewa yaron ya kama lobster kuma ya yi farin ciki, sai ya fahimci cewa yana kururuwa "Ka cije ni!"
Ya cije ni!
