An yi wa Erdogan baƙar fata a birnin Cologne
A ranar Asabar (29 ga watan Satumba), mun ga murmushi da kuma sarari mai launin shuɗi yayin da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka gana don karin kumallo a Berlin.
Ranar ta kasance ranar ƙarshe ta ziyarar da shugaba Erdogan ya kai Jamus, wadda ta yi ta neman gyara dangantakar da ke tsakanin 'yan kawancen NATO.
An yi watsi da dangantakar abokantaka saboda matsalolin da suka shafi 'yancin bil'adama,' yancin kafofin watsa labarai da kuma karbar Turkiyya cikin EU.
