Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala sakamakon zalunci da kuma fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Kowace kuri'a da aka kada wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, kuri'a ce da ta ki amincewa da dabarun da suka fi na jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taro a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya bayyana cewa Kavanaugh ya sha wahala sakamakon zalunci da kuma fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da ya tsaya takarar shugabancin kasar.
Kavanaugh ya shaida wa majalisar dattawa a ranar Alhamis, inda ya musanta zargin da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi masa na cin zarafin da aka yi mata shekaru da dama da suka gabata a lokacin da suke matasa.
Ford ya kuma ba da shaida a lokacin da ake sauraron karar.
Shugaban ya yi sanarwa a ranar Asabar cewa, a yau, jama'ar Amurka sun shaida kwarewar Kavanaugh, kwarin gwiwarsa da kuma halayensa.
"Duk wani kuri'a da aka kada wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, kuri'a ce da aka jefa wa daya daga cikin manyan masu shari'a na wannan karni, lauya na gaskiya da ke da kyakkyawan suna a hidimar jama'a", in ji shugaban kasar a gaban taron masu goyon baya daga West Virginia.
Shugaban ya yi magana a kai tsaye game da takarar Kavanaugh yayin da yake magana game da mahimmancin kuri'un Republican a babban zaben.
"Akwai makonni biyar da suka rage kafin wani babban zabe na zamaninmu.
"Duk da cewa ni ba dan takara ba ne, amma ni na shiga cikin wannan takara", in ji Trump.
"Wannan shi ne dalilin da ya sa nake tafiya da kuma yin gwagwarmaya don tallafa wa 'yan takara masu kyau".
Trump ya ce dimokiradiyya na da manufa ta "hanawa da kuma hanawa".
