Shekara: Wanda ya ƙirƙira na'urar lissafin Geiger
Shafi na mujallarmu ta ranar Lahadi: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, ranar da aka haifi wanda zai zama masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wanda hakan ya kai ga samar da na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
