A yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai tara dubun dubatan mutane a babban filin wasa a Central Park, wanda ba wai kawai za su ji daɗin yin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Sean Mendes ba, amma kuma za su fahimci ainihin manufar taron - kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekarar 2030.
Bikin  Global Citizen wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012 ci gaba ne na  Global Poverty, wani kungiya mai kare hakkin bil'adama da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta na taron (sai dai idan ba ku son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halarta sun yi wasu ayyuka ko aiki kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kira ko kuma yin hulɗa ta wata hanya don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar "Mutumin Duniya" yake shekaru 12 kafin ya cimma burinsa?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da yin wasa kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta shawo kan mutane su nemi a yi wani abu ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "klictivism" da mutane suke tunanin cewa suna yin wani abu mai ma'ana sa'ad da suka sanya hannu a takarda ta intanet ko kuma suka aika wani sakon Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya rubuta fiye da miliyan 19 na ayyukan masu goyon bayansa, suna neman abubuwa daban-daban.
Ya ce, waɗannan ayyuka sun taimaki shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 zuwa 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta kawo ambaton alkawura 390 da sanarwar da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda a cikinsu aka biya ko aka tara akalla dala biliyan 10.
Ƙungiyar ta ce kuɗin da aka ba da sun riga sun shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da  Power of Food, wani kamfani da aka kafa a Burtaniya tsakanin masu zuba jari da masu sana'a,  Help Children Develop their Full Potential, wanda ya yi alkawarin baiwa Rwanda dala miliyan 35 domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar, bayan karbar sakonni sama da 4,700 a shafin Twitter daga  'yan kasa da kasa  .
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin tarihi", in ji jakadan "Power of Food" Tracy Ullman a wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki matakai sama da 5,000 da ke kira ga Burtaniya ta inganta ciyar da uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade ga wani shiri, "The Power of Nursing", wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan biyar.
A amsa ga wani daga cikin masu ba da agaji a shafinsa na yanar gizo, yana tambaya "Me ya sa kuke ganin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci?"
"Mutumin Duniya" ya amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala, wani lokacin za mu kasa kuma wani lokacin za mu sake kasawa.
Amma kamar yadda aka yi a manyan ƙungiyoyin 'yancin jama'a da na nuna wariyar launin fata kafin mu, za mu yi nasara domin muna da ƙarfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Sean Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Mona wasu ne daga cikin masu yin bikin na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborah-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
