Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da aka yi a tsakiyar shekara.
A lokacin taron majalisar gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin tsayawa takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su zo Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci game da shugaban kasa Donald Trump a majalisar dattijai, yana mai cewa yana kai kasar nan ga hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina damuwa sosai kamar yadda Donald Trump yake damuwa game da dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ta yi magana a fili game da Trump da kuma wanda ya tsaya takara a kan kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
