Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da tayar da hankali ta hanyar tallar farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka game da amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa da aka bayar ta China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa  bayan ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Peking na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben 'yan majalisar wakilai na Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne a cikin yunkurin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don inganta cinikayya, a yanzu haka, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani, inda suke daidaita harajin shigo da kayayyaki tsakanin ƙasashe.
Masana daga Amurka da China sun ce a farkon yakin cinikayya, an tsara takunkumin da aka sanya wa kasar Sin ne don a gurgunta masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni barazana.
China, in ji Branstad a cikin wata sanarwa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, "yana ninka wannan zalunci ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da kuma 'yancin latsawa ta hanyar saka talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"Akwai bambanci, a kan kantin sayar da jaridu a kan titi a nan birnin Beijing, za ku ga 'yan maganganu kaɗan kuma ba za ku ga ainihin nuna ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen Sin ke da su game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin tsananin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jaridar kasar Sin ta kauce wa bayar da labarin, duk da cewa ba ta bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Da rasuwar Kavanaugh, 'yan Republican sun hana mata kada kuri'a a zaben fidda gwani, manazarta sun gargadi
Da yake manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon bayan da kuma kare wanda aka zaba a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh kan zargin cin zarafin mata da dama, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a samu martani, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben da ke tafe.
An samu tashin hankali sosai game da wannan batu kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun ce suna son a ci gaba da zaben.
Ba za a iya mayar da waɗannan abubuwa baya ba, in ji Grant Raher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, ga The Hill a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Raher ya ce yana shakkar cewa bukatar da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi a lokacin karshe na gudanar da bincike daga FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karin Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington.
A safiyar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun yi ihu "Nuwamba na zuwa!" a yayin zanga-zangar da suka yi a cikin harabar majalisar dattawa, yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasius Ford ya bayar, in ji Mic.
"Za a cire himmar dimokiradiyya da kuma muradinsa", in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai sharhi kan siyasa.
"Mutane suna cewa matsalar ta yi tsanani; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi muni, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin unguwannin gari da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, tsakanin shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a saboda ba sa son shugaban kasa.
Tun kafin Ford ta gabatar da shaidar ta bayyana zargin da ta yi wa wanda ya zaɓa a kotun koli, manazarta sun ce za a iya samun martani idan 'yan Republican suka nace a amince da takarar.
"Wannan ya zama babban rikici ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun batun zaben kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma ko an jefa Kavanaugh ne a kotu, amma batun yadda 'yan Republican ke magance wannan lamarin da kuma yadda suke bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, kungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma jama'ar Amirka sun nuna cewa sun rabu a kan wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, suna karkata zuwa ga na biyu.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin 100 sun ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin wataƙila ko kuma tabbas Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce Ford ya yi hakan.
Bayan da Flake ya bukaci a yi haka, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma na wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, kamar yadda jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da take shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a lokacin da suke wani biki a lokacin da take karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin fara sabuwar intanet domin ya kai hari ga Google da Facebook
Mai kirkiro na Yanar gizo Tim Berners-Lee ya fara wani shiri da zai yi takara da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da wata almara ta fasaha ta yi, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke gina dandalin buɗe tushen Burners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da ke da izinin samun damar wasu bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ta yi wa'azin cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da aikin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid, wanda ke bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar  ɗakunan ajiya na kan layi na sirri ko POD.
Yana ɗauke da jerin abubuwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sana'a da na sirri.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify, wanda za ka iya samun damar yin amfani da shi a kowane browser, kuma duk suna aiki a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne yake zaɓan wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke cikin bayanan.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "sarrafa bayanan sirri".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shi ne kamfanin ya zuba jari da albarkatu, da hanyoyin da kuma basira da suka dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A yanzu kamfani ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu ci gaba da suka yi kwangila don su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma wasu masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi canji ko a'a, lokacin da duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya sake fasalin su cikin dare.
